#lang narscribblus/interactive

@title{Popups}

A widget that wants to display a pop-up needs to say so in the widget
definition.
@exSlice["name-widget" nil #:depth 0 #:expand "popups"]

It needs to tell us:
@itemize[
  @item{
    What it wants to display.
    @exslice["name-widget" "details" #:depth 1 #:expand "constraint"]
  }
  @item{
    How the pop-up should look.
  }
  @item{
    How the pop-up should behave.
    @exslice["name-widget" "details" #:depth 1 #:expand "clickAway"]
  }
  @item{
    Where to display it.
    @exslice["name-widget" "details" #:depth 1
             #:expand "position"
             #:expand "centerOnFocus"]
  }
]

